---
import Rhoms from "@/components/Rhoms.astro";
---

<section id="concept" class="relative">
  <div class="concept-container container-base relative h-svh w-svw bg-main">
    <div class="concept-content grid grid-rows-3 h-full">
      <div class="concept-tit self-end">
        <h1 class="text-white text-[28px]"><span class="block pb-3 pl-1">小さなカケラから</span>
          <span class="text-5xl inline-block pr-2">大きな幸せ</span>を</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="concept-txt text-white row-start-3 ">
        <p><span class="font-en tracking-wider pr-0.5">such</span>として<br class="lg:hidden">個人でWebサイト制作を<br class="lg:hidden">行なっています。</p>
        <p>想いやりの心を大切に、<br class="lg:hidden">丁寧なお仕事を心がけています。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="concept-img absolute top-3/7 w-3/5 right-1.5">
      <img src="./images/hand.png" alt="幸せのカケラを拾う手" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
    </div>
  </div>
  <Rhoms />
</section>
